StrictHostKeyChecking ask
UseRoaming no
SendEnv LANG LC_*


## WUSTL servers
Host htcf.wustl.edu htcf
    HostName htcf.wustl.edu
    Port 22
    User liang-bo.wang


Host genomic.wustl.edu genomic
    Hostname genomic.wustl.edu
    User lwang


Host shell.cec.wustl.edu shell
    Hostname shell.cec.wustl.edu
    User liang-bo.wang


## Ding Lab servers
